<p align="right" style="margin-top: .75em; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35em;">Support the journalists that have been fighting back against dangerous disinformation since day one: </p>
<p align="right" style="margin-top: .75em; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35em;">Give what you can to keep us publishing.</p>
